  <brief_title>Effect of Oral Vitamin D3 on Chronic Rhinosinusitis Treatment in Adults With Lower Vitamin D Levels</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Oral Vitamin D3 on Wound Healing After Endonasal Endoscopic Sinus Surgery for Chronic Rhinosinusitis With Nasal Polyposis and Lower Vitamin D Levels</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>The First Affiliated Hospital of Shanxi Medical University</agency>
